entries.arrived_at_delivery: One of our Car'das agents will be there momentarily to pick up the information you found off the Black Sun spy.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Thank you, pilot. We'll process this information immediately. You did well out there.
entries.found_loc_d: Pilot, I'm transmitting the location at which you'll meet our agent for the drop off. Head there as soon as possible. I want to get this information to our intelligence agency as quickly as we can.
entries.hello_d: Agent Rayar here. Dock with me when you're ready. I'll need to get that information to our intelligence agency soon.
entries.quest_dock2_d: 'It should be simple to give the information to Agent Rayar. All I have to do is dock with him and he'll be able to download the information off my systems. --To dock with another vessel, target it and press the 'U' key. When the docking process has been completed, your computer systems will alert you.'
entries.quest_location_d: 'Ord Mantell... Heart of the Bright Jewel.'
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: 'Member of the Car'das intelligence ring, Agent Rayar has come to Ord Mantell space to pick up the encoded information that I had found on the Black Sun spy. The details found within must be of great important to the Car'das and I am itching to find out why.'
entries.split_quest_alert: Laetin A'shera: <Time to return home pilot...>
entries.title: Black Sun Infiltration: The Delivery
entries.title_d: 'Laetin will be appreciative to receive the encoded information I have in my systems. It seems to have been a hot ticket with the Black Sun. I'm hoping I won't have to tangle with them for quiet some time. I gather, however, that I'll be seeing them more than my wits, and my hull, can handle. But if they want a fight, I'll be there. After I complete my mission, I should head back to the Tansarii Point Station. I'll need to communicate with her to get permission to land. --You can communicate with a Space Station by targeting it and typing /comm in your spatial chat.--'
